// Cadence Supabase Configuration
// Copy this file to Config.xcconfig and fill in your values.
// Config.xcconfig is gitignored and must not be committed.
//
// Required keys:
//   1. Your Supabase project URL
//   2. Your Supabase anonymous/public key
